      "specificArticles": [
        {
          "textContent": "<br><b>Hiking trail of about 4 hours and 15km long.</b><br> Over 100 lakes were built to be used in gold mining processing. Some exists also today and are very nice and relaxing places that can be visit along this trail. Start from Casa Petri, head to 'Tarina' (the farmlands of Rosia Montana) and stop at the Tarina Lake and at the Weather Station from the 'Rotundu' Peak. From here go to the 'Tăul Mare' lake and to the Lety și Sulei massif. Have a break, enjoy the view and return to the historic center along the 'Corna' and 'Brazi' lakes."
        }
      ]
